{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/java-nio/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"FDW-blog","author":"kimifdw"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"e185c3a0-85fc-5869-a25b-a36622f00f26","html":"<h1 id=\"reactor模型\"><a href=\"#reactor%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>reactor模型</h1>\n<h2 id=\"单线程reactor模型\"><a href=\"#%E5%8D%95%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8Breactor%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>单线程reactor模型</h2>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/421140a893b6c175fb2de990d928e793/9d5da/single-thread-reactor.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/421140a893b6c175fb2de990d928e793/fcda8/single-thread-reactor.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/421140a893b6c175fb2de990d928e793/12f09/single-thread-reactor.png 148w,\n/static/421140a893b6c175fb2de990d928e793/e4a3f/single-thread-reactor.png 295w,\n/static/421140a893b6c175fb2de990d928e793/fcda8/single-thread-reactor.png 590w,\n/static/421140a893b6c175fb2de990d928e793/9d5da/single-thread-reactor.png 871w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<h3 id=\"java-nio-support\"><a href=\"#java-nio-support\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>java nio support</h3>\n<ol>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Channels</code>。连接文件、socket等支持非阻塞读取</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Buffers</code>。表示直接从<code class=\"language-text\">channels</code>中读取或写入的数组对象</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Selectors</code>。表示哪些<code class=\"language-text\">Channel</code>集合存在IO事件</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">SelectionKeys</code>。用于维持IO事件的状态和绑定关系</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"多线程单reactor模型\"><a href=\"#%E5%A4%9A%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B%E5%8D%95reactor%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>多线程单reactor模型</h2>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8cdd2d87c311e51d6e70f4fa04173e58/c0255/worker-thread-pool-reactor.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 76.35135135135135%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/8cdd2d87c311e51d6e70f4fa04173e58/fcda8/worker-thread-pool-reactor.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8cdd2d87c311e51d6e70f4fa04173e58/12f09/worker-thread-pool-reactor.png 148w,\n/static/8cdd2d87c311e51d6e70f4fa04173e58/e4a3f/worker-thread-pool-reactor.png 295w,\n/static/8cdd2d87c311e51d6e70f4fa04173e58/fcda8/worker-thread-pool-reactor.png 590w,\n/static/8cdd2d87c311e51d6e70f4fa04173e58/efc66/worker-thread-pool-reactor.png 885w,\n/static/8cdd2d87c311e51d6e70f4fa04173e58/c0255/worker-thread-pool-reactor.png 920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<ul>\n<li>工作线程。reactors需要快速触发handlers,非IO处理转移到其他线程上</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"多线程多reactor模型\"><a href=\"#%E5%A4%9A%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B%E5%A4%9Areactor%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>多线程多reactor模型</h2>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d41c6f6b9f88f13da54bf6d50f0f6671/efc66/multiple-reactors.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 80.4054054054054%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/d41c6f6b9f88f13da54bf6d50f0f6671/fcda8/multiple-reactors.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d41c6f6b9f88f13da54bf6d50f0f6671/12f09/multiple-reactors.png 148w,\n/static/d41c6f6b9f88f13da54bf6d50f0f6671/e4a3f/multiple-reactors.png 295w,\n/static/d41c6f6b9f88f13da54bf6d50f0f6671/fcda8/multiple-reactors.png 590w,\n/static/d41c6f6b9f88f13da54bf6d50f0f6671/efc66/multiple-reactors.png 885w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<ul>\n<li>由主acceptor分配到其他reactor去处理</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"nio其他功能\"><a href=\"#nio%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>nio其他功能</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>支持每个reactor包含多个selectors，简单流程介绍如下：向一个Selector中注册了Channel后，由selector自动来判断查询这些channel是否有已就绪的IO事件</li>\n<li>文件转移。自动化从文件到网络或网络到文件的拷贝</li>\n<li>内存文件映射。利用<code class=\"language-text\">buffers</code>来处理文件，<code class=\"language-text\">channel</code>总是从<code class=\"language-text\">Buffer</code>中读取数据或写入数据</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Buffer</code>。数据是通道读入缓冲区，从缓冲区写入到通道中的。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>流程。写入数据到buffer——>调用flip()方法【读写切换】——>从buffer中读取数据——>数据清理clear()/compact()</li>\n<li>\n<p>工作原理。\n\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7e2690d1ce27bb69075e82223c9733cf/065e2/buffer-mode.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 577px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 64.86486486486486%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/7e2690d1ce27bb69075e82223c9733cf/065e2/buffer-mode.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7e2690d1ce27bb69075e82223c9733cf/12f09/buffer-mode.png 148w,\n/static/7e2690d1ce27bb69075e82223c9733cf/e4a3f/buffer-mode.png 295w,\n/static/7e2690d1ce27bb69075e82223c9733cf/065e2/buffer-mode.png 577w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 577px) 100vw, 577px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<ol>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">capacity</code>。缓冲区的固定大小。</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">position</code>。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>写操作。当前位置，初始化为0，最大为capacity-1</li>\n<li>读操作。读取特定位置读，写模式切换到读模式，position重置为0</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">limit</code>。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>写操作。最多能往buffer里写多少数据</li>\n<li>读操作。最多能读到多少数据，能读到position的数据</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Direct buffers</code>。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>支持零拷贝；</li>\n<li>在开启或结束时有开销，所分配的内存不在JVM堆上；</li>\n<li>用于长连接。</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Non-Direct Buffer</code>。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>直接在JVM堆上进行内存的分配。本质为byte[]数组</li>\n<li>存在内存拷贝问题，效率低</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Channel</code>类型</p>\n<ol>\n<li>FileChannel：文件操作【同步】</li>\n<li>DatagramChannel：UDP操作</li>\n<li>SocketChannel：TCP操作</li>\n<li>ServerSocketChannel：TCP操作，使用在服务器端</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Channel事件</code></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Connect, 即连接事件(TCP 连接), 对应于SelectionKey.OP_CONNECT</li>\n<li>Accept, 即确认事件, 对应于SelectionKey.OP_ACCEPT</li>\n<li>Read, 即读事件, 对应于SelectionKey.OP_READ, 表示 buffer 可读.</li>\n<li>Write, 即写事件, 对应于SelectionKey.OP_WRITE, 表示 buffer 可写.</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Selector</code>的基本使用流程\n\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6833fde3b57f1f0f993183df648e0c85/83e77/nio-server-sequence.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 56.75675675675676%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/6833fde3b57f1f0f993183df648e0c85/fcda8/nio-server-sequence.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6833fde3b57f1f0f993183df648e0c85/12f09/nio-server-sequence.png 148w,\n/static/6833fde3b57f1f0f993183df648e0c85/e4a3f/nio-server-sequence.png 295w,\n/static/6833fde3b57f1f0f993183df648e0c85/fcda8/nio-server-sequence.png 590w,\n/static/6833fde3b57f1f0f993183df648e0c85/efc66/nio-server-sequence.png 885w,\n/static/6833fde3b57f1f0f993183df648e0c85/83e77/nio-server-sequence.png 889w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<ol>\n<li>通过<code class=\"language-text\">Selector.open()</code>打开一个<code class=\"language-text\">Selector</code>.</li>\n<li>将<code class=\"language-text\">Channel</code>注册到<code class=\"language-text\">Selector</code>中, 并设置需要监听的事件(interest set)</li>\n<li>\n<p>不断重复:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>调用<code class=\"language-text\">select()</code>方法</li>\n<li>调用<code class=\"language-text\">selector.selectedKeys()</code>获取selected keys</li>\n<li>迭代每个 selected key:</li>\n<li>从<code class=\"language-text\">selected key</code>中获取 对应的<code class=\"language-text\">Channel</code>和附加信息(如果有的话)</li>\n<li>判断是哪些 IO 事件已经就绪了, 然后处理它们. <strong>如果是 OP_ACCEPT 事件, 则调用 “SocketChannel clientChannel = ((ServerSocketChannel) key.channel()).accept()” 获取 SocketChannel, 并将它设置为 非阻塞的, 然后将这个 Channel 注册到 Selector 中.</strong></li>\n<li>根据需要更改 selected key 的监听事件.</li>\n<li>将已经处理过的 key 从 selected keys 集合中删除.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>","timeToRead":4,"frontmatter":{"title":"java nio selector","date":"October 26, 2020","spoiler":"reactor模型"},"fields":{"slug":"/java-nio/"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/java-nio/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/go-assembly/","directoryName":"go-assembly"},"frontmatter":{"title":"plan9 assembly 完全解析【转】"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/epoll/","directoryName":"epoll"},"frontmatter":{"title":"epoll 介绍"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["336482444"]}